The paper deals with deep generative models of images and their performance on downstream tasks, specifically classification accuracy. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, given that the paper focuses on image classification, it is more likely to belong to cs.LG and cs.CV.
